description:
THE BEST WAY to HIDE your PHOTOS and VIDEOS behind a CALCULATOR !
What everyone can see is just an ordinary calculator.
Until you type in your secret passcode it became a private storage app in which you can hide your most secret photos, videos, and more.

Some of the featured offered are:
1) Easy to use:
Fully functioning that you can add your ‘SPECIAL’ photos&videos into Calculator
, we provides many convenient ways:
1. From Photo App(Camera Roll) ;
2. From iTunes File Sharing Sync;
3. From Cloud Drive;
4. From in App Camera;

2) Security:
1. Secret passcode is needed when access photo & video privacy;
2. Folder passcode - Further protection to keep people out of your private folders;
3. Hidden Folder - Special way to make files&folders invisible;


3) More than you can imagine:
1.You can hide all your private photos, contacts, passwords, notes.
2. Send files via email;
3. Back up your photos, videos and other files
4. Multiple formats Support:
5.Private web browser with autofill your password to login if you need.
